---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Card, CardContent, CardHeader, CardTitle, CardDescription } from '@/components/ui/card';
import { Badge } from '@/components/ui/badge';
import { Separator } from '@/components/ui/separator';
---

<Layout title="평가방법 - IMAS">
  <!-- Header -->
  <section class="border-b border-border/40 py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 text-center">
      <Badge variant="outline" className="mb-4 text-[#4a9eff] border-[#4a9eff]/40">Assessments</Badge>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight md:text-5xl">5가지 인체공학 평가</h1>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-muted-foreground">
        국제적으로 인정받는 표준 평가 방법을 자동으로 수행합니다
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pose-based -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
      <div class="mb-10 flex items-center gap-3">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">자세 기반 평가</h2>
        <Badge variant="secondary" className="text-xs">실시간 자동</Badge>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <!-- RULA -->
        <Card className="border-border/60 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="md:flex">
            <div class="border-b border-border/40 bg-[#4ade80]/5 p-6 md:w-64 md:border-b-0 md:border-r">
              <Badge className="bg-[#4ade80]/20 text-[#4ade80] border-0 mb-3">무료</Badge>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">RULA</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground">Rapid Upper Limb Assessment</p>
              <div class="mt-4 text-xs text-muted-foreground">McAtamney & Corlett, 1993</div>
            </div>
            <CardContent className="flex-1 p-6">
              <p class="mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                상지(팔, 손목) 중심의 반복 작업에서 발생할 수 있는 근골격계 질환 위험을 평가합니다.
                컴퓨터 작업, 조립 라인 등 상지 반복 작업에 적합합니다.
              </p>
              <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
                <div class="rounded-lg bg-muted/50 p-3">
                  <div class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">점수 범위</div>
                  <div class="font-semibold">1 ~ 7점</div>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-lg bg-muted/50 p-3">
                  <div class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">위험 수준</div>
                  <div class="font-semibold">4단계</div>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-lg bg-muted/50 p-3">
                  <div class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">평가 부위</div>
                  <div class="font-semibold">상박, 전완, 손목, 목, 몸통, 다리</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </CardContent>
          </div>
        </Card>

        <!-- REBA -->
        <Card className="border-border/60 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="md:flex">
            <div class="border-b border-border/40 bg-[#4a9eff]/5 p-6 md:w-64 md:border-b-0 md:border-r">
              <Badge className="bg-[#4a9eff]/20 text-[#4a9eff] border-0 mb-3">등록</Badge>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">REBA</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground">Rapid Entire Body Assessment</p>
              <div class="mt-4 text-xs text-muted-foreground">Hignett & McAtamney, 2000</div>
            </div>
            <CardContent className="flex-1 p-6">
              <p class="mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                RULA를 확장하여 전신 자세와 외부 부하를 종합적으로 평가합니다.
                의료/보건 분야에서 자주 사용되며, 하체 자세까지 포함한 전신 부하를 분석합니다.
              </p>
              <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
                <div class="rounded-lg bg-muted/50 p-3">
                  <div class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">점수 범위</div>
                  <div class="font-semibold">1 ~ 12점</div>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-lg bg-muted/50 p-3">
                  <div class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">위험 수준</div>
                  <div class="font-semibold">5단계</div>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-lg bg-muted/50 p-3">
                  <div class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">평가 부위</div>
                  <div class="font-semibold">목, 몸통, 다리, 상완, 전완, 손목</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </CardContent>
          </div>
        </Card>

        <!-- OWAS -->
        <Card className="border-border/60 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="md:flex">
            <div class="border-b border-border/40 bg-[#4a9eff]/5 p-6 md:w-64 md:border-b-0 md:border-r">
              <Badge className="bg-[#4a9eff]/20 text-[#4a9eff] border-0 mb-3">등록</Badge>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">OWAS</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground">Ovako Working Posture Analysis</p>
              <div class="mt-4 text-xs text-muted-foreground">Ovako Oy, 1977</div>
            </div>
            <CardContent className="flex-1 p-6">
              <p class="mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                작업 자세를 4자리 코드(등/팔/다리/하중)로 분류하여, 작업 자세의 유해성을 빠르게 평가하는 분류 시스템입니다.
                현장에서 간편하게 적용할 수 있습니다.
              </p>
              <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
                <div class="rounded-lg bg-muted/50 p-3">
                  <div class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">코드 구성</div>
                  <div class="font-semibold">4자리 자세 코드</div>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-lg bg-muted/50 p-3">
                  <div class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">조치 등급</div>
                  <div class="font-semibold">AC1 ~ AC4</div>
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-lg bg-muted/50 p-3">
                  <div class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">코드 항목</div>
                  <div class="font-semibold">허리, 상지, 하지, 무게</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </CardContent>
          </div>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Task-based -->
  <section class="border-t border-border/40 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
      <div class="mb-10 flex items-center gap-3">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">작업 기반 평가</h2>
        <Badge variant="secondary" className="text-xs">수동 입력</Badge>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
        <!-- NLE -->
        <Card className="border-border/60 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="border-b border-border/40 bg-[#4a9eff]/5 p-6">
            <Badge className="bg-[#4a9eff]/20 text-[#4a9eff] border-0 mb-3">등록</Badge>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">NLE</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground">NIOSH Lifting Equation</p>
            <div class="mt-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground">NIOSH, 1993</div>
          </div>
          <CardContent className="p-6">
            <p class="mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              들기 작업에서 작업자가 안전하게 들 수 있는 최대 무게(RWL)를 계산하여 들기 작업 위험도를 평가합니다.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
              <div class="rounded-lg bg-muted/50 p-3">
                <div class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">입력값</div>
                <div class="text-sm font-semibold">수평거리, 수직높이, 이동거리, 비틀림, 빈도, 손잡이</div>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-lg bg-muted/50 p-3">
                <div class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">결과값</div>
                <div class="text-sm font-semibold">RWL(kg), 리프팅 지수(LI)</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </CardContent>
        </Card>

        <!-- SI -->
        <Card className="border-border/60 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="border-b border-border/40 bg-[#4a9eff]/5 p-6">
            <Badge className="bg-[#4a9eff]/20 text-[#4a9eff] border-0 mb-3">등록</Badge>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">SI</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground">Strain Index</p>
            <div class="mt-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground">Moore & Garg, 1995</div>
          </div>
          <CardContent className="p-6">
            <p class="mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              상지 반복 작업의 위험도를 6가지 작업 요인의 승수 값 곱으로 산출하는 누적 외상성 질환(CTD) 평가입니다.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
              <div class="rounded-lg bg-muted/50 p-3">
                <div class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">입력값</div>
                <div class="text-sm font-semibold">강도, 지속시간, 빈도, 손목 자세, 작업 속도, 하루 지속시간</div>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-lg bg-muted/50 p-3">
                <div class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">결과값</div>
                <div class="text-sm font-semibold">SI 점수 (3 미만: 안전, 7 이상: 위험)</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </CardContent>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Risk Levels -->
  <section class="border-t border-border/40 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6">
      <h2 class="mb-8 text-center text-2xl font-bold">위험 수준 색상 체계</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:grid-cols-4">
        {[
          { color: 'bg-[#4ade80]', label: '안전', desc: '정상 작업 자세' },
          { color: 'bg-[#facc15]', label: '주의', desc: '추가 조사 필요' },
          { color: 'bg-[#fb923c]', label: '경고', desc: '개선 필요' },
          { color: 'bg-[#f87171]', label: '위험', desc: '즉시 개선' },
        ].map((level) => (
          <Card className="border-border/60 text-center">
            <CardContent className="pt-6">
              <div class={`mx-auto mb-3 h-4 w-4 rounded-full ${level.color}`}></div>
              <div class="font-semibold">{level.label}</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">{level.desc}</div>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
